com.gwtplatform.dispatch.rest.shared

Interface RestDispatch

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RestDispatchAsync

    public interface RestDispatch
    An asynchronous dispatcher service with an arbitrary action type. The actions will be sent over HTTP using a REST architecture.
